00:27:01,412 --> 00:27:03,039
Matagal na kitang hinahanap.

455
00:27:03,122 --> 00:27:05,541
Umupo tayong lahat.

456
00:27:08,919 --> 00:27:11,672
Ano ba 'to?
Anong meron sa maingay na kapaligiran?

457
00:27:11,756 --> 00:27:13,549
May namatay ba o ano?

458
00:27:15,801 --> 00:27:17,470
Wala ako sa mood para magbiro.

459
00:27:18,512 --> 00:27:19,347
Kaya ka iniwan.

460
00:27:20,514 --> 00:27:21,682
Alam mo…

461
00:27:22,933 --> 00:27:24,685
Kaya susuko ka na lang?

462
00:27:26,395 --> 00:27:27,271
Ako…

463
00:27:28,272 --> 00:27:29,774
ayaw mong sumuko kay Yoon!

464
00:27:30,399 --> 00:27:31,484
Uy, Jae Min.

465
00:27:31,567 --> 00:27:33,444
Ano? Ano ang masasabi mo?

466
00:27:33,527 --> 00:27:34,653
Sumpa man.

467
00:27:34,737 --> 00:27:36,113
Uy, Yoon.

468
00:27:36,197 --> 00:27:38,449
Hindi mo na ba talaga makikita
ulit si Si-on?

469
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:40,034
Siyempre ikaw nga.

470
00:27:40,117 --> 00:27:42,078
Ikaw rin, Tae-ha.

471
00:27:42,161 --> 00:27:43,954
Maaari ka bang maging masaya

472
00:27:44,038 --> 00:27:45,247
kapag malungkot si Yoon?

473
00:27:55,716 --> 00:27:56,926
Sabay-sabay tayong lumipat dito!

474
00:27:58,886 --> 00:27:59,929
Ha?

475
00:28:00,513 --> 00:28:02,098
-Tayong lahat?
-Hindi naman malaking bagay 'yon.

476
00:28:03,349 --> 00:28:04,392
Mamuhay tayong lahat nang sama-sama.

477
00:28:05,476 --> 00:28:08,020
Makikilala mo lang nang lubusan ang isang tao
pagkatapos mong magsama sa bahay.

478
00:28:08,813 --> 00:28:09,647
Ganyan

479
00:28:11,107 --> 00:28:12,441
makikita mo ang tunay nilang ugali.

480
00:28:14,110 --> 00:28:16,654
Gayunpaman, hindi pa rin
natin kailangang mamuhay nang magkakasama.

481
00:28:17,488 --> 00:28:18,739
Natatakot ka ba?

482
00:28:18,823 --> 00:28:19,657
Tapos sumubsob.

483
00:28:19,740 --> 00:28:20,991
Huwag kailanman!

484
00:28:22,618 --> 00:28:23,494
May tiwala rin ako.

485
00:28:25,871 --> 00:28:26,956
Mukhang hindi ito tama--

486
00:28:27,039 --> 00:28:28,707
Tumahimik ka!

487
00:28:29,667 --> 00:28:30,584
Tumahimik ka!

488
00:28:31,168 --> 00:28:32,002
Huwag kang mag-alala,

489
00:28:32,086 --> 00:28:34,588
ang aking maliit na batang usa.

490
00:28:34,672 --> 00:28:36,006
Ano?

491
00:28:36,632 --> 00:28:37,633
Magiging sobrang saya ito.

492
00:28:39,635 --> 00:28:40,594
Kasayahan?

493
00:28:41,345 --> 00:28:42,430
Magiging impyerno ito.

494
00:28:46,434 --> 00:28:47,560
Simula na ba ito ng ikalawang round?

495
00:28:51,355 --> 00:28:52,565
Sige, tara na!

496
00:28:53,190 --> 00:28:55,526
Sa ating tahanan, mahal na tahanan!

497
00:28:55,609 --> 00:28:57,403
Yeah! Putok, putok!

498
00:28:57,486 --> 00:28:59,071
Tara na!

499
00:29:09,832 --> 00:29:14,462
PINAKASIKAT NA NOBELANG WEBEL NG 2026 NA
WE WERE FRIENDS

500
00:29:14,545 --> 00:29:17,673
HULING KABANATA:
UNANG NIYEBE

501
00:29:18,257 --> 00:29:19,341
Sinta,

502
00:29:19,425 --> 00:29:21,218
kailan ito kinunan?

503
00:29:22,094 --> 00:29:23,762
Naku, grabe.

504
00:29:23,846 --> 00:29:26,724
Doon ako pumunta sa ER
dahil sa food poisoning.

505
00:29:27,391 --> 00:29:28,309
Ang IS?

506
00:29:30,227 --> 00:29:34,732
Yung paulit-ulit mo akong pinapakain ng hilaw na talaba,
sinasabi mong mabuti raw ang mga iyon para sa aking lakas.

507
00:29:34,815 --> 00:29:35,816
Lalaki.

508
00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:38,027
Ah, yung panahon na nasa Seoul tayo?

509
00:29:53,250 --> 00:29:54,293
Ano ang nagdala sa iyo rito?

510
00:29:56,170 --> 00:29:57,630
Aalis ka bukas, 'di ba?

511
00:29:57,713 --> 00:29:59,006
Tapos ka na bang mag-empake?

512
00:29:59,632 --> 00:30:01,759
Oo. Nandito ka ba para magpaalam?

513
00:30:04,595 --> 00:30:06,222
Nandito ako para ibigay ito sa iyo.

514
00:30:14,146 --> 00:30:17,274
Nabalitaan kong napakamahal ng mga bayarin sa ospital sa Amerika ,

515
00:30:17,358 --> 00:30:20,194
at maaaring mahirap makakuha
ng gamot. Paano kung magkasakit ka?

516
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:24,657
Huwag kang magkasakit.

517
00:30:24,740 --> 00:30:28,536
At huwag kang masyadong lumapit kay Deul-i
habang naroon ka.

518
00:30:28,619 --> 00:30:32,414
Pero isa pa, huwag ka
ring masyadong lumapit sa kahit sinong babaeng Amerikano.

519
00:30:32,915 --> 00:30:35,459
Mag-focus ka lang sa studies mo, ha?

520
00:30:36,126 --> 00:30:37,378
Gayundin,

521
00:30:37,461 --> 00:30:39,880
Mag-ingat sa mga magagandang babaeng Amerikano...

522
00:30:40,464 --> 00:30:44,260
at pati na rin ang mga guwapong Amerikano.

523
00:30:44,343 --> 00:30:48,305
Kung may kumausap sa iyo,
huwag mo silang nginitian pabalik.

524
00:30:48,389 --> 00:30:49,431
Okay?

525
00:30:52,059 --> 00:30:53,018
Salamat.

526
00:30:55,604 --> 00:30:57,815
Iyon mismo ang ngiting
tinutukoy ko.

527
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:00,442
Magiging isang kalamidad ito.

528
00:31:02,736 --> 00:31:05,447
Mananatili ka lang sa US
habang nagbabakasyon

529
00:31:05,531 --> 00:31:07,283
